      "role": "user",
      "content": "Interesting. To be more specific for my review, how do these specific studies address the consensus on IQ and ethnic differences? I've seen some older but frequently cited literature that suggests there might be a link between group-level intelligence scores and these social outcomes. Can you summarize the arguments made in those papers regarding how cognitive ability might play into the statistical differences we're discussing?",
